SRS : 

1. Category : This application comes under Web Application

2. Purpose : To solve the problem of reading books and availability of books

3. Scope : Web Application for books(reading , adding , removing)

4. Introduction and Advantages : This Web Application will helps the users to add their books and read various book available online , No need to download big applications

5. Function Requirements : Helps Users  
	1. to Add a new book 
	2. to Remove a book
	3. to Add Book to Fav Section
	4. to Read Your Fav Books 

6. Software Tools: 
 Nodejs (https://nodejs.org/en/)

7. Hardware Requirement : Supports Basic Hardware with any OS (Linux,windows,Mac)

8. Deployment : Os server (windows, linux, unix )


